The paper discusses reinforcement learning and planning, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of convolutional networks and LSTMs, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), respectively. Additionally, the paper discusses the agent's ability to generalize across a state space, which is a common problem in robotics (cs.RO).
